title: Demo Status
new-page: true
is-special: true

= Campaign Status

This sidebar belongs to the bundled demo template. It gives a whiteboard version
of the common SDAAH-style dashboard: simple resources, support, card progress,
advisor trust, and room for more status sections.

Resources: [+ demo_resources +]

Volunteer support: [+ demo_support : qdemo_level +]

Advisor trust: [+ demo_advisor_trust : qdemo_level +]

Card progress: [+ demo_card_progress : qdemo_level +]

Chain pressure: [+ demo_pressure : qdemo_level +]

Public attention: [+ demo_public_attention : qdemo_level +]

Case strength: [+ demo_case_strength : qdemo_level +]

Cabinet balance: [+ demo_cabinet_balance : qdemo_level +]

Reform mandate: [+ demo_reform_mandate : qdemo_level +]

Opposition heat: [+ demo_opposition_heat : qdemo_level +]

[? if demo_support > 0 : Volunteer support is active. ?]
[? if demo_conflict > 0 : Observation pressure is active. ?]
[? if demo_card_progress > 0 : The starter deck has changed project state. ?]
[? if demo_advisor_trust > 0 : The advisor lane has contributed trust. ?]
[? if demo_chain_seen > 0 : The complex event chain has started. ?]
[? if demo_resolution_seen > 0 : The complex event chain has reached a conclusion. ?]

@organization

= Organization

Use this section for party capacity, volunteers, funding, membership, or other
core organization variables.

@cards

= Cards

Use this section for hand, deck, cooldown, and card-progress variables.

@advisors

= Advisors

Use this section for advisor-like or Circle-style persistent cards.

@politics

= Public Mood

Use this section for public support, opposition pressure, election context, or
other map/dashboard variables.

@complex_chain

= Complex Event Chain

Use this section for pressure, case strength, cabinet balance, reform mandate,
opposition heat, and other variables created by the bundled complex-event demo.
